kagu (1.0.10) unstable; urgency=low

  * Headphone sense - music paused/unpaused when headphones are plugged/unplugged
  * Made save playlist combo-shortcut work in all screens
  * Added history-combo to save playlist dialog
  * Added playlist shuffling/randomization, removed random playback mode
  * Added Settings menu to group settings together
  * Added Auto-play toggle to Settings menu
  * Added Genres screen
  * Album/Artist/Genre lists now show item counts
  * Now Playing cover image fallback, to show the artist image if no cover found
  * Option to choose between artist or album images in Now Playing button and Cover screen
  * Added year display to album list
  * Added sort by year option to Settings
  * Startup time improvements
  * Added confirmation dialog to Playlist Clear button
  * Scanner now ignores hidden files and directories
  * Delete playlist option to Playlists screen
  * Chinook installation and operation fixes
  * Added notification for missing files
  * Added headset button support to toggle playback (Chinook only)
  * Added sleep timer activation notification
  * Turn off screen option removed, will be back in a later version
  * Added DBus signals for playback notifications
  * Added Music menu

 -- Kemal Hadimli <disqkk@gmail.com>  Fri, 16 Nov 2007 18:00:00 +0300

