kagu (1.0.9) unstable; urgency=low

  * New theme!
  * Added 2-hour option to Sleep Timer
  * Made heuristic cover search optional in Scanner
  * Artist grouping changed, utilizing the "album artist" tag if it exists
  * Artist and album names are normalized to Title Case
  * Hold thumb at NowPlayingButton and hit the dpad center for Playlist Save As, only available in Now Playing
  * Hold thumb at NowPlayingButton and hit the menu key to jump to artist songs/albums functionality, works almost anywhere
  * Added default player selection to main menu (available only if mplayer is installed)
  * Cover art load times are faster, and no longer a black screen
  * Various other startup time optimizations
  * Added scrollbars
  * Performance and UI enhancements

 -- Kemal Hadimli <disqkk@gmail.com>  Mon, 15 Oct 2007 15:00:00 +0300

kagu (1.0.8) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add artist images to Artists View
  * New theme!
  * Added Sleep Timer and Turn Off Screen options to the menu
  * Added Playlist View, Scanner now also scans for playlists
  * Added volume button, changed Volume View
  * WMA and AAC support
  * Added key combos, hold thumb at NowPlayingButton and use the dpad for actions
  * Remove one from playlist option (via dedicated icon, or combo+dpadcenter)
  * Added key combo to re-arrange songs in the playlist (Combo+dpad up or combo+dpad down to move selected song up or down)
  * Scanner: Made scans incremental, added option to do a full scan
  * Scanner: Update artist and album names from AudioScrobbler (if possible)
  * Scanner: Recursion depth increased
  * Scanner: Added --batch-mode option
  * Moved database and covers to ~/.kagu
  * Crash logs now saved to MyDocs
  * Plenty of bugfixes
  * Performance and UI enhancements

 -- Kemal Hadimli <disqkk@gmail.com>  Mon, 17 Sep 2007 21:10:00 +0300

